%h4 Forgot Password?
%p
  If you have forgotten your password, click #{link_to "here", new_password_path(resource_name)}.

%h4 Account locked?
%p
  If your account has been locked, please click #{link_to "here", new_unlock_path(resource_name)}.

%h4 Confimation pending?
%p
  Please remember to confirm the account within #{Devise.confirm_within.inspect}. If you would like to receive the confirmation email again, click #{link_to "here", new_confirmation_path(resource_name)}.